'''Mark A. Clark''' ([[March 8]], [[1967]] -) born in [[San Manuel, Arizona]], is member of the [[United States Democratic Party|Democratic Party]].  

He was a state representative in the [[Arizona]] House of Representative's 45th Legislature (District 07) from [[2001]] to [[2002]].  His father, [[Harry Clark (politician)|Harry Clark]], was a state representative from [[1992]] - [[2000]]. 

In [[2003]], [[United States Republican Party|Republican]] [[Jim Waring]] became representative of District 07.
		

